{"tid":1658333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭正式向港人宣戰","createTime":"2019-10-16T12:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T13:05:02.000Z","uid":73959,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e61119faa42436beabda53179cbd6f6e021146","tid":1658333,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"本身我都覺得佢係依戀權貴<br />\n但今日施政報告一岀<br />\n我肯定林鄭決心同我哋攬抄<br />\n因為佢知道佢已經係罪人<br />\n全世界都知佢有幾陰毒、有幾柒<br />\n一向自視過高，連考第三都會喊<br />\n佢已經再抬唔起頭做人<br />\n啲中同大學同學指住佢笑<br />\n林鄭心諗既然你哋班人想攬炒吖嘛<br />\n佢就真。攬炒<br />\n香港人，請做好心理準備<br />\n未來會更黑暗<br />\n唔好唔好再對呢個政府有期望<br />\n只有抱住真。攬炒心態<br />\n先至可以痛快結束<br />\n<br />\n你哋寧願繼續溫水煮蛙<br />\n定係痛快搏一舖？"},{"pid":"ad88efd3f8ae3cf53c0a3203bea2cb719ddedbfb","tid":1658333,"uid":201680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"10月20日 大遊行 13億人民站起來！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跪求文宣進場幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國戰線好重要</span></span>"},{"pid":"bfc799930a275c345ec3db4f3f02444f79d4c996","tid":1658333,"uid":60868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"6月9號晚已經宣左戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74115406b1872cf164d955620efa38f79c91af97","tid":1658333,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"Kill kill kill kill burn burn burn burn"},{"pid":"b454f567ad665794d185e215e21e2eccf6d514fa","tid":1658333,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc799930a275c345ec3db4f3f02444f79d4c996","tid":1658333,"uid":60868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite